{"word":"φημί","slug":"φημί","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>φημί</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ IE\">IE</a>, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ Lat.\">Lat.</a> for (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ inf.\">inf.</a> fari) ‘speak, talk’] ‘convey one’s thinking through verbal communication’, whether orally (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> in dialogue) or in writing<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp> say <a href='B:470 4:7'>Mt 4:7</a>; <a href='B:470 8:8'>8:8</a>; <a href='B:480 14:29'>Mk 14:29</a>; <a href='B:490 7:40'>Lk 7:40</a>; <a href='B:490 23:40'>23:40</a>; <a href='B:500 18:29'>J 18:29</a>; <a href='B:510 2:38'>Ac 2:38</a>; <a href='B:510 19:35'>19:35</a>; <a href='B:510 22:2'>22:2</a>; <a href='B:510 26:25'>26:25</a>; <a href='B:530 6:16'>1 Cor 6:16</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> in clarification or explanation of what one has stated <b>say, mean <a href='B:530 7:29'>1 Cor 7:29</a>; <a href='B:530 10:15'>10:15</a>; <a href='B:530 15:50'>15:50</a>; imply <a href='B:530 10:19'>10:19</a>; claim <a href='B:520 3:8'>Ro 3:8</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:φήμη\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:φημίζω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}